The paper deals with optimization problems and approximation algorithms for non-monotone submodular functions and monotone subadditive functions under partition matroid constraints. This falls under the category of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and game theory (cs.GT).
